# Backend Structure

The backend is built using Convex, a full-stack development platform:

## Schema

[convex/schema.ts](mdc:convex/schema.ts) defines the database schema.

## User Types

- **Participant**: Code in [convex/participant/](mdc:convex/participant) handles participant-specific logic
- **Organizer**: Code in [convex/organizer/](mdc:convex/organizer) handles organizer-specific logic

## Authentication

Authentication is configured in [convex/auth.config.ts](mdc:convex/auth.config.ts) and [convex/auth.ts](mdc:convex/auth.ts).

## Common Utils

[convex/common/](mdc:convex/common) contains utilities shared across different parts of the backend.

## HTTP Endpoints

[convex/http.ts](mdc:convex/http.ts) defines HTTP endpoints for external integrations.
